name: TWISTER I-3 STILL
description:
TWISTER I-3.
Still from TWISTER I-3 animation (OBJKT#165485), keyframe 31, 2500x2500 jpeg. 
Initially minted in 10 copies.

TWISTERS is a project about inconstant and changeable human nature and about different ways people may react to something that doesn't fit their expectations. TWISTERS is the original series of abstract animated artworks by Olga Feldman.
